productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Georgie has one of these. She works as a busboy and she says it looks brown.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 yard and weights 19 pound!!!
I tried to hang it but got jelly bean all over it.
This Web works outstandingly well. It beautifully improves my basketball by a lot.
i use it centenially when i'm in my greenhouse.
